#. lang="pi"><section class="sutta" id="thag2.2"><article><div
#. class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "thag2.2:1.1"
msgid "Theragāthā"
msgstr "Verses of the Senior Monks"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "thag2.2:2.1"
msgid "Dukanipāta"
msgstr "The Book of the Twos"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "thag2.2:3.1"
msgid "Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "Chapter One"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag2.2:4.1"
msgid "2.2. Piṇḍolabhāradvājattheragāthā"
msgstr "2.2. Piṇḍolabhāradvāja"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc123"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts123"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.2:5.1"
msgid "“Nayidaṃ anayena jīvitaṃ,"
msgstr "You can’t live by fasting,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.2:5.2"
msgid "Nāhāro hadayassa santiko;"
msgstr "but food doesn’t lead to peace of heart."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.2:5.3"
msgid "Āhāraṭṭhitiko samussayo,"
msgstr "Seeing how this bag of bones is sustained by food,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.2:5.4"
msgid "Iti disvāna carāmi esanaṃ."
msgstr "I wander, seeking."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc124"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts124"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.2:6.1"
msgid "Paṅkoti hi naṃ pavedayuṃ,"
msgstr "They know it’s just a swamp,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.2:6.2"
msgid "Yāyaṃ vandanapūjanā kulesu;"
msgstr "this homage and veneration in respectable families."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.2:6.3"
msgid "Sukhumaṃ sallaṃ durubbahaṃ,"
msgstr "Honor is a subtle dart, hard to extract,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.2:6.4"
msgid "Sakkāro kāpurisena dujjaho”ti."
msgstr "and hard for a sinner to give up."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag2.2:7.1"
msgid "Itthaṃ sudaṃ āyasmā piṇḍolabhāradvājo thero gāthāyo abhāsitthāti."
msgstr ""
"It was thus that these verses were recited by the senior venerable "
"Piṇḍolabhāradvāja."
